72, \"to\": 3735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3610, \"end\": 3618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7003791630303286e-22, \"text\": \"Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 3626, \"end\": 3635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.090433184233659e-16, \"text\": \"Louis XVI\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XVI\"}, {\"begin\": 3640, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5482248512157406e-42, \"text\": \"Marie Antoinette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}, {\"begin\": 3721, \"end\": 3734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999996561282979, \"rank\": 3.438722216698508e-07, \"text\": \"freestyle BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding and 3x3 basketball are here, too, part of the Games' push to attract a younger, urban audience, the competitions themselves only part of the spectacle at what, between events, feels more like a family fun day.\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3x3 basketball\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3768}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' push\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"a younger, urban audience\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitions\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"only part\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacle\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"a family fun day\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the number of children here giving new sports a crack, it is working.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3975}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3987}, {\"ngram\": \"new sports\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4010}, {\"ngram\": \"a crack\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The point here is not just about what Paris has tried to do, but that they have done it brilliantly - and London ought to take note.\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4074, \"end\": 4079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.946598209494589e-32, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4142, \"end\": 4148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999317879, \"rank\": 6.800471706938136e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The point\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"note\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the capital is serious, as Mayor Sadiq Khan said last week it is, about bringing the Games back in 2040 this must be the model.\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4205, \"end\": 4215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadiq_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sadiq Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadiq_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadiq_Khan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4262}, {\"ngram\": \"the model\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just 28 years on from London 2012, there will be no need to build fresh, grand facilities.\", \"from\": 4301, \"to\": 4391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4323, \"end\": 4334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4404507896057794e-14, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no need\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4357}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh, grand facilities\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, one of the major positives of that Games' legacy remains the absence of white elephants.\", \"from\": 4392, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the major positives\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"Games' legacy\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4448}, {\"ngram\": \"the absence\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"white elephants\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But nor should it set out to imitate a summer that now, in the rose-tinted national memory, exists as a beacon of unattainable harmonious ideal.\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a summer\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4534}, {\"ngram\": \"the rose-tinted national memory\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4579}, {\"ngram\": \"a beacon\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"unattainable harmonious ideal\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2040 Games would have to be their own, in story and, where reasonable, in stage.\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2040 Games\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4649}, {\"ngram\": \"story\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"stage\", \"from\": 4713, \"to\": 4718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If athletics, cycling and swimming would likely return to their 2012 homes, then go and build a skatepark in Trafalgar Square.\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4754}, {\"ngram\": \"their 2012 homes\", \"from\": 4778, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"a skatepark\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4825}, {\"ngram\": \"Trafalgar Square\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take climbing - booming in popularity among young Londoners - into the Royal Albert Hall, archery into the gardens of Buckingham Palace, judo into Shakespeare's Globe.\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 5014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4924, \"end\": 4930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"score\": 0.9999999989540811, \"rank\": 1.0457799021920628e-09, \"text\": \"Albert\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uncle_Albert\"}, {\"begin\": 4994, \"end\": 5005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.025532039394554e-18, \"text\": \"Shakespeare\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"popularity\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4884}, {\"ngram\": \"young Londoners\", \"from\": 4891, \"to\": 4906}, {\"ngram\": \"archery\", \"from\": 4937